These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  police-officer, nurse, software-developer, project-manager, doctor, coach, chef
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, russian, french, brazilian, indonesian, german, malaysian
 1. the project-manager is on the left of the brazilian##1
 2. the indonesian is the project-manager##1
 3. the chef is on the right of the coach##1
 4. the french is on the right of the german##1
 5. the software-developer is in the middle##1
 6. the colombian is on the far left##1
 7. the doctor is the colombian##1
 8. the police-officer is on the right of the german##1
 9. the french is on the left of the russian##1
10. the brazilian is on the left of the software-developer##1
11. the chef is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | doctor | project-manager | nurse | software-developer | police-officer | coach | chef |
| Nationality   | colombian    | indonesian   | brazilian      | german | french    | russian    | malaysian         |

