.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: lettuce, broccoli, apple, onion, papaya, spinach, strawberry
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, indie, electronic, hip-hop, reggae, country, r&b
 1. the fan of reggae is the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the fan of country is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 9. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating apple##1
10. the person eating onion is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | lettuce | broccoli | papaya | onion | spinach | strawberry | apple |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | electronic   | hip-hop   | reggae      | blues       | r&b       | country     |

