.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: raspberry, cabbage, pumpkin, banana, eggplant, zucchini, potato
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, musician, architect, coach, manager, firefighter, engineer
 1. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the engineer##1
 3. the musician is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 4. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the dressmaker is the person eating eggplant##1
 6. the architect is on the right of the musician##1
 7. the musician is on the left of the architect##1
 8. the musician is on the right of the coach##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is the coach##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the dressmaker##1
11. the coach is in the middle##1
12. the person eating potato is on the left of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | cabbage | eggplant     | pumpkin  | zucchini       | raspberry       | potato  | banana   |
| Job    | firefighter  | dressmaker | engineer | coach | musician | architect | manager |

