.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, pop, funk, d&b, country, soul, trance
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, german, dutch, malaysian, canadian, mexican, russian
 1. the fan of country is the german##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 3. the mexican is on the right of the dutch##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
 7. the dutch is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the right of the mexican##1
 9. the fan of funk is the canadian##1
10. the canadian is on the left of the fan of pop##1
11. the russian is the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | trance     | d&b     | funk      | pop | country      | electronic     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | dutch | mexican | canadian | russian | german | pakistani |

