.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: rock-climbing, ponying, reading, puzzles, skydiving, card-games, dancing
7 different pets are kept: bird, pony, mouse, rat, ferret, goat, hamster
 1. the person who's hobby is ponying is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 3. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is ponying##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | ponying | reading | card-games     | puzzles | dancing | skydiving | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | hamster   | mouse    | ferret | goat     | bird         | rat     | pony        |

