.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, water, tea, mirinda, fanta, milk
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, train, helicopter, airplane, boat, snowmobile, van
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the van##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | water | fanta   | hot-chocolate | tea | milk  | mirinda | cola |
| Transport   | airplane   | boat | roller | snowmobile     | train | van | helicopter   |

