.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, horror, western, family, romance, spy, fantasy
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, tram, car, ship, van, quad-bike
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | fantasy | family | romance | spy     | horror | western |
| Transport     | van | car      | quad-bike | tram    | ship | airplane   | taxi  |

